                                                           BUSINESS QUESTION
Are frequent visitors actually becoming buyers?

                                   QUERY
SELECT
login_frequency,
ROUND(AVG(total_purchases),2) AS avg_purchases
FROM ecommerce_data
GROUP BY login_frequency
ORDER BY login_frequency;

                                 Insight:
Customers with higher login frequency tend to have higher purchases, showing that engagement increases the chances of buying, but it does not guarantee it.

                          Recommendation:
We should keep the platform active and engaging so customers keep coming back, which can increase the chances of them purchasing.
